n Speakers to Identify L2 Consonants and Vowels: A Short-Term High Variability Training Study. Retrieved February 27, 2021, from http://doe.concordia.ca/copal/documents/8_Carlet_Cebrian_Vol5.pdf%0a%0a%0a[[#contentends]]%0a----%0a(:Category:)%0a(:GradedBy: :)
